                    in the <literal>OpenStack User Guide</literal>.</paragraph>
                <paragraph>For information about disk and container formats for images, see
                    <reference name="Disk and container formats for images" refuri="https://docs.openstack.org/image-guide/image-formats.html">Disk and container formats for images</reference>
                    in the <literal>OpenStack Virtual Machine Image Guide</literal>.</paragraph>
